column2: SELECT TOP #   e.SystemStudentID as StudentID,   e.GradeLevel as EnrollmentGrade,   e.SchoolYear4Digit as SchoolYear4Digit,   t.TestPeriod as Period,   t.TestSubjectGroup as AssessmentSubject,   &&& as MetricSource,   t.TestType as MetricName,   t.TestScore as Score,   t.TestDate as IsMostRecent FROM Enrollment as e   JOIN TestScores as t   ON e.SystemStudentID = t.SystemStudentID
